      • UserComment

      • AutoComment

        public static final EActionType AutoComment
        Comment created by a program or script.

      • VersionCreated

        public static final EActionType VersionCreated
        Document version created. An action of this type is automatically created by the system, if a new document version is checked in and this version is not set as the work version.

      • WorkVersionCreated

        public static final EActionType WorkVersionCreated
        Document work version created. An action of this type is automatically created by the system, if a new version of a non-release document is checked in and this version is set as the work version.

      • WorkVersionSwitched

        public static final EActionType WorkVersionSwitched
        Document work version switched. An action of this type is automatically created by the system, if the work version of a non-release document is set and no content is uploaded.

      • Released

        public static final EActionType Released
        Document work version switched. An action of this type is automatically created by the system, if the work version of a release document is set.
        See Also:
        SordDetails.isLimitedReleaseDocument()

      • SordCreated

        public static final EActionType SordCreated
        Sord created. An action of this type is automatically created by the system when the feed is initialized. The create date is set to the archiving date. For documents, member Action.docVersion represents the first version.
        Since:
        9.00.000.013
        See Also:
        Action.docVersion, Action.docVersionGuid
